 up enough heat, this Pokemon'sbody temperature can reach up to 1700 degrees.</td></tr><tr><td class="red">Red</td><td class="text" rowspan="2">When storing thermal energy in its body, itstemperature could soar to over 1600 degrees.</td></tr><tr><td class="blu">Blue</td></tr><tr><td class="yel">Yellow</td><td class="text" rowspan="1">It has a flame chamber inside its body. It inhales,then blows out fire that is over 3,000F degrees.</td></tr>
